Not surprised USAC is doing this. They’ve shown time and time again that they’re not to be trusted with such large sums of student money. Yet they keep asking for more $$$. Not this time.

Gosh, this is a bad look for them. Didn’t they at least consider the backlash this could cause? Totally a bad time to ask for money.
I laughed for like 3 straight minutes. Lol thank you.
